perl-File-Find-Rule
-------------------------------------------
File::Find::Rule is a friendlier interface to File::Find. It allows you 
to build rules which specify the desired files and directories.

Runtime requirements:
  perl-5.10.0-3
  perl-Number-Compare-0.01-2
  perl-Text-Glob-0.08-1

Canonical homepage:
  http://search.cpan.org/~rclamp/File-Find-Rule/

Canonical download:
  http://www.cpan.org/authors/id/R/RC/RCLAMP/

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  unpack perl-File-Find-Rule-0.30-X-src.tar.bz2
    if you use setup to install this src package, it will be
	 unpacked under /usr/src automatically
  cd /usr/src
  cygport ./perl-File-Find-Rule-0.30-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/perl-File-Find-Rule-0.30-X-src.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/perl-File-Find-Rule-0.30-X.tar.bz2

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

  /usr/bin/findrule
  /usr/lib/perl5/vendor_perl/5.10/File/Find/Rule.pm
  /usr/lib/perl5/vendor_perl/5.10/File/Find/Rule/Extending.pod
  /usr/lib/perl5/vendor_perl/5.10/File/Find/Rule/Procedural.pod
  /usr/lib/perl5/vendor_perl/5.10/i686-cygwin/auto/File/Find/Rule/.packlist
  /usr/share/doc/perl-File-Find-Rule-0.30/Changes
  /usr/share/doc/perl-File-Find-Rule-0.30/README
  /usr/share/man/man1/findrule.1.gz
  /usr/share/man/man3/File.Find.Rule.3pm.gz
  /usr/share/man/man3/File.Find.Rule.Extending.3pm.gz
  /usr/share/man/man3/File.Find.Rule.Procedural.3pm.gz

